                        <interp inst="t18391216-name-106" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN PARK</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I stopped the prisoner in Charlotte-street on Wednesday morning about a quarter to ten o'clock.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I know nothing about it—it was six. o'clock when I got up.</p>
